  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK207">
<l>eṉaippakai yuṟṟāru muyvar viṉaippakai</l>
<l>vīyātu piṉceṉ ṟaṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>However great be the enmity men have incurred they may still live. The enmity of sin will incessantly pursue and kill.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
